track_notes:
The trail leads along a well-wired mountain path, crosses the ski slope and ends at the end station of the gondola to Rifugio Lagazuoi. From here, the path to the top again continues along the path approx. 10 minutes of moderate walking. At the top of the hill, there is enough space for antenna.
On way back down it`s about 2 hours of moderate walk.
track_title: Path from Cable car on Falzarego Pass and back on the Lagazuoi trail
